from\": 285, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"the village's notorious level crossing\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading TheHarris Gates railway crossing on the Olympic Highway, about three kilometres east of Illabo, will be removed and an overpass put in, sharing in a $70 allocation in the 2024-25 state budget.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Illabo\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Loginor\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 354}, {\"ngram\": \"TheHarris Gates railway crossing\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Highway\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"about three kilometres\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"an overpass\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"a $70 allocation\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024-25 state budget\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray Norman's farm is not going to be affected by the project, which changes his perspective on the matter as he understands the impacts it will have on some other landowners.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"score\": 0.9999999999445208, \"rank\": 5.561919717825965e-11, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\"}, {\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"his perspective\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"the impacts\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"some other landowners\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are on the side unaffected by it but the farms on the other side are being greatly affected,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"the farms\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you are in the farms where it's going through, it's hideous.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the farms\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a complicated issue.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a complicated issue\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The farms it goes through and the areas the crossing goes through need to be cared for and need to be thought through.\\\"\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"The farms\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"the areas\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"the crossing\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"need\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That being said, money being put into smaller communities is important.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller communities\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Money needs to be put in so those communities do not get short changed,\\\" Mr Norman said.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Money\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"those communities\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's cutting farms up which is not great but it does also provide the means of providing a railway between Melbourne and Brisbane.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Cross_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.789342185541195, \"rank\": 0.26686523443487187, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Cross_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Cross_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999406725815565, \"rank\": 5.889278837911148e-05, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"farms\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"the means\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"a railway\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Definitely we would see it as a positive, it's a great infrastructure project.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great infrastructure project\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If our farm was on the other side then that would not be good.\\\"\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our farm\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Norman said it is no secret level crossings are notoriously dangerous and the site of many crashes.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no secret level crossings\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"many crashes\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Harris Gates level crossing is no different.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Harris Gates level crossing\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Level crossings are dangerous.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Level crossings\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been accidents on level crossings,\\\" Mr Norman said.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"accidents\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"level crossings\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As they are building the railway it is good for the crossings to be fixed, to be worked through, the government does also need to work towards a budget across the whole line as well.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the railway\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"the crossings\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"a budget\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole line\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we are going to produce food for the world, if we are going to have industry inland, if we can not transport it you can not have industry, you can not have production and the government making these bold steps is really important for local communities.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"industry\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"industry\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"production\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"these bold steps\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"local communities\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we want jobs, if we want prosperity in the regions, in the bush, we have to expect that when the government puts up opportunities like this we have to support it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"prosperity\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"the regions\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"the bush\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His son Tom Norman is of a similar mind, welcoming the project.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2392, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Norman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Norman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.